  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_restrictive_intervention_post_incident_review">Restrictive Intervention Post-Incident Review</xref>
 is a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_activity">CARE ACTIVITY</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_restrictive_intervention_post_incident_review">Restrictive Intervention Post-Incident Review</xref>
 is a meeting conducted by the healthcare 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>
 following an incident of a 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_restrictive_intervention">Restrictive Intervention</xref>
 to identify and address any physical harm to the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 or 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_care_personnel">Care Personnel</xref>
, ongoing risks, and the emotional impact on the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 or 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_care_personnel">Care Personnel</xref>
.  </p>

